"I don't know.  I haven't seen him since we got back from the cave."
She turned and looked over at Quickstrike. She sighed for she knew he 
would be in no condition to fight for a while yet.
"I have a strange ship on the monitor, and right now, it's just you, 
me,SCorponok and Drillbit.  The others are out and I don't know when 
they will get back.  KitKat is back at the vok cave looking for Rowdy 
Wolf. I just hope she returns in one piece."
